{"tid":1832731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢專家組成員王廣發向本台證實確診新型肺炎","createTime":"2020-01-21T11:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T15:23:33.000Z","uid":53062,"like":247,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"d7c73e92584e5d5c80f4b0fda3450c8b9bbc208f","tid":1832731,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:13:30.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】內地疫情擴情擴散，連去武漢實地調查的專家都受到感染。國家衛健委武漢肺炎專家組成員王廣發向我們證實，已確診染上武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n王廣發是北大第一醫院呼吸和危重症醫學科主任醫師，國家衛健委專家組早前曾去武漢了解疫情，王廣發曾在10日接受過中央電視台訪問時，指病毒的致病性較弱，疫情仍可控。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/15964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F15964&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6mvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=874cfa0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F15964&h=e997a655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/15964</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n算唔算社會主義鐵拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5b5787528333c7258a799e2c53117209ab37ac","tid":1832731,"uid":53062,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"參考資料<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/PDChinese/status/1215724995374206976?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPDChinese%2Fstatus%2F1215724995374206976%3Fs%3D09&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6mvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=183337e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPDChinese%2Fstatus%2F1215724995374206976%3Fs%3D09&h=226f693e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/PDChinese/status/1215724995374206976?s=09</a><br />\n 【國家醫療專家組專家解讀武漢不明原因肺炎：致病性較弱，情況可控】近日引起廣泛關注的武漢不明原因的病毒性肺炎已初步判定是由一種新型冠狀病毒引起。國家醫療專家組專家、北京大學第一醫院呼吸和危重症醫學科主任醫師王廣發稱，目前來看該病毒的致病性較弱，病患病情和整體疫情處於可控狀態。"},{"pid":"58550ca6e1bd09c99c45753a59ef8f3b10069c82","tid":1832731,"uid":225798,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:15:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2020 中國瓦解</span>"},{"pid":"514b615db6475e2d5653d27939e90b3f350cb775","tid":1832731,"uid":108016,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:15:35.000Z","msg":"多謝党"},{"pid":"67e11ac4e3a830e5b49dec24bd1ae2d94c643677","tid":1832731,"uid":79563,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:15:59.000Z","msg":"同2003年沙士既傳染模式100%一樣<br />\n<br />\n超級帶菌者【劉劍倫】就係當年調查組專家"},{"pid":"68b63cbf6712baf4ec5f8092c19121cf865d2e27","tid":1832731,"uid":288707,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:16:14.000Z","msg":"讓領導先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc85c60e66c6d7a68abcc77506a29d00baf2954","tid":1832731,"uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/9XZD8hm0/image.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2F9XZD8hm0%2Fimage.png&h=ad5ef550&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50ce7814bb30cb8aec376b544f56c48a234da7ce","tid":1832731,"uid":280752,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:16:37.000Z","msg":"又話無問題可以控制到既? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec5640670f4d7ae495d29b42b37399d5bcbf474","tid":1832731,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c5b5787528333c7258a799e2c53117209ab37ac","tid":1832731,"uid":53062,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"參考資料<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/PDChinese/status/1215724995374206976?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPDChinese%2Fstatus%2F1215724995374206976%3Fs%3D09&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6mvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=183337e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPDChine