id":1832731,"uid":209746,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBR7GKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBR7GKS.jpg&h=9cd13b94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db65ff0ccfa026ffdac38971993a9a769abe203","tid":1832731,"uid":235477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:46:13.000Z","msg":"没事儿<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfae9b14d022154c2070e8c6e12f4a5472ccce1","tid":1832731,"uid":271545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:49:23.000Z","msg":"以身試毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953cddb61a49894a2bb7f6a679479d8971e64e88","tid":1832731,"uid":74171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"SARS：<br />\n- 該病最早於2002年11月16日在中國廣東順德爆發<br />\n- 2003年2月11日上午，廣州市政府召開新聞發布會公布廣州地區非典型肺炎情況，稱<strong>所有病人的病情均在控制當中</strong>。[9]強調對於廣州千萬人口300多人染病是個很小的比例，非典型肺炎只是局部發生...<br />\n-2003年2月21日，染病的中山大學附屬第二醫院（孫逸仙紀念醫院）退休教授劉劍倫至香港出席親屬的婚禮，並入住香港京華國際酒店911號房，並且將疾病傳染給另外七名旅客。劉劍倫其後於2月22日往廣華醫院急症室求診並在3月4日不治去世。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎：<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n-最早病例出現於2019年12月8日<br />\n- 2020年1月中：內地專家王廣發-新型冠狀病毒<strong>整體疫情可控</strong><br />\n<br />\n次撚次都係可控，結果搞到四圍都係先正視個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c0296dbfdab4900a1d95cf836a23f7608f8019","tid":1832731,"uid":189875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:49:43.000Z","msg":"武漢有險可守"},{"pid":"2601e81c636720abd1fc50a98479a7ade0e18d6b","tid":1832731,"uid":40439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:50:37.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒<img src=\"/asset